title: zephz Youth Tumble Cheerleading Shoe
features: Lightweight synthetic upper with embroidered logo
Red, yellow, green, blue and black laces included
Foam cushioned EVA midsole and rubber outsole with stunt heelTM
description: The zephz Tumble Cheerleading Shoe features a lightweight synthetic leather upper with embroidered logo for a clean, sleek look. Includes 5 additional lace colors (red, blue, green, yellow, black) so you can show your team pride. The thermoplastic heel counter, rubber outsole with stunt heel and an EVA midsole offer the necessary support to carry you through the season.
